#| Runs after:                                                                 |
#|  - .zshenv                                                                  |
#|  - .zshlogin                                                                |
#|  - .zshprofile                                                              |
#|                                                                             |
#| Sourced by:                                                                 |
#|  ✅ login shells                                                            |
#|  ✅ non-login shells                                                        |
#|  ✅ interactive        ←───── The focus of this script.                     |
